author: veithen
msg: Improving the JSON code - Step 2 - Instead of using some hacks to extract the name of the element, just let Axiom determine it lazily using the feature introduced by AXIOM-399.
This should make databindings work with Badgerfish (although we have no integration test for this yet) and solve AXIS2-5158, AXIS2-5295 and AXIS2-5300.
